cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "QML Agent Lab"
message: "If you use QML Agent Lab in your work, please cite this repository."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: "Dillon"
repository-code: "https://github.com/Aggredicus/qml-agent-lab"
url: "https://github.com/Aggredicus/qml-agent-lab"
abstract: >
  QML Agent Lab is a lightweight agent operating system for designing,
  implementing, evaluating, and documenting quantum machine learning
  experiments in AI-assisted development workflows. It emphasizes classical
  baselines, reproducible comparison, modest claims, and agent-readable
  experiment artifacts.
keywords:
  - quantum machine learning
  - QML
  - AI agents
  - machine learning
  - reproducibility
  - benchmarking
  - Qiskit
  - PennyLane
license: MIT
version: "0.1.4"
date-released: "2026-04-25"
